sample_comments.text:
Pro- food was very good
Cons-
Staff were rude; 
Housekeeping didn't clean the cups in the room twice (I even put rubbish in it for the second day hoping that would indicate it needed washing, but there was still milk in it);
Room wasn't available for checkin at 14:00;
I couldn't find my membership card, and the checkin staff didn't want to / couldn't check my number so I applied again, checked the receive communications in English box, and have had three emails entirely written in Thai. Shame really as I've stayed in other hotels in this group without problems.
